00:17:31.360 --> 00:17:32.200
Fang Lihen

00:17:36.160 --> 00:17:38.160
Fang Lihen!

00:17:39.840 --> 00:17:40.680
Hua Xiaofei

00:17:41.520 --> 00:17:43.280
Don't take another step forward.

00:17:43.280 --> 00:17:44.240
Leave now.

00:17:44.520 --> 00:17:45.960
Immediately.

00:17:47.000 --> 00:17:48.720
What happened to Fang Lihen?

00:17:49.000 --> 00:17:50.800
Why is he lying there motionless

00:17:51.120 --> 00:17:52.650
with a white cloth over him?

00:17:53.200 --> 00:17:53.880
Fang Lihen!

00:17:55.960 --> 00:17:56.760
Hua Xiaofei!

00:17:57.960 --> 00:17:59.840
From the first day you arrived in Chang'an

00:17:59.840 --> 00:18:00.880
until today,

00:18:00.880 --> 00:18:02.680
nothing good has happened.

00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:05.480
You nearly cost me my job

00:18:06.280 --> 00:18:08.540
and caused this tragedy to happen to Ali.

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:10.020
Do you have a heart?

00:18:10.960 --> 00:18:12.360
Everything you do

00:18:12.360 --> 00:18:13.960
is only for your own benefit.

00:18:15.880 --> 00:18:16.440
I...

00:18:16.760 --> 00:18:18.680
I never meant to harm Fang Lihen.

00:18:19.240 --> 00:18:22.440
Yesterday you told Ali that you admired him.

00:18:25.720 --> 00:18:26.240
Yes.

00:18:26.480 --> 00:18:27.280
Then why

00:18:27.440 --> 00:18:29.440
did you flirt with Young Master Ying today?

00:18:29.440 --> 00:18:31.960
You triggered Young Master Ying's gynophobia again.

00:18:31.960 --> 00:18:34.760
Ali felt his sincere feelings were betrayed

00:18:34.880 --> 00:18:36.080
and set fire in anger.

00:18:36.160 --> 00:18:36.960
I swear,

00:18:37.920 --> 00:18:40.520
I truly had no intention of harming Fang Lihen.

00:18:42.200 --> 00:18:43.600
Everything I did

00:18:43.960 --> 00:18:45.360
was out of necessity.

00:18:46.400 --> 00:18:47.400
Out of necessity?

00:18:47.960 --> 00:18:48.960
You blame everything

00:18:48.960 --> 00:18:50.520
on necessity.

00:18:50.680 --> 00:18:52.140
Where is your bottom line?

00:18:52.160 --> 00:18:53.620
Where is your conscience?

00:18:53.960 --> 00:18:55.420
You're so greedy for money

00:18:55.760 --> 00:18:57.020
that you'd kill for it.

00:18:57.400 --> 00:18:59.400
You don't deserve to be loved at all.

00:19:01.160 --> 00:19:02.220
I don't deserve it?

00:19:03.600 --> 00:19:04.840
I've tried so hard.

00:19:04.960 --> 00:19:05.720
Tried hard?

00:19:07.120 --> 00:19:09.200
You've only tried hard to murder for money.

00:19:09.200 --> 00:19:10.600
All you care about is money.

00:19:10.600 --> 00:19:11.240
I think

00:19:12.200 --> 00:19:13.840
you'll be lucky not to be punished by heaven.

00:19:13.840 --> 00:19:16.300
I admit I sometimes use unscrupulous means.

00:19:16.520 --> 00:19:18.520
I admit it and I'm willing to change.

00:19:18.960 --> 00:19:19.960
But I swear,

00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:20.960
I absolutely had

00:19:20.960 --> 00:19:22.960
no intention of harming Fang Lihen.

00:19:23.160 --> 00:19:24.000
If I did,

00:19:25.440 --> 00:19:27.680
may I be struck by lightning.

00:19:32.360 --> 00:19:33.920
Hua Xiaofei! Hua Xiaofei!

00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:52.240
Li.

00:19:53.000 --> 00:19:55.000
Was I too harsh with my words?

00:19:55.480 --> 00:19:58.410
I can't believe it summoned lightning to strike her.

00:19:58.720 --> 00:19:59.960
Am I dreaming?

00:20:01.400 --> 00:20:02.760
The strike was very real.

00:20:02.760 --> 00:20:03.960
She was even smoking.

00:20:05.360 --> 00:20:06.040
This...

00:20:07.440 --> 00:20:08.160
The two of us

00:20:08.160 --> 00:20:10.020
only wanted to teach her a lesson.

00:20:10.440 --> 00:20:12.570
How could it bring divine punishment?

00:20:12.720 --> 00:20:14.250
The doctor said she's fine.

00:20:15.120 --> 00:20:16.760
Just probably fainted from exhaustion.

00:20:16.760 --> 00:20:17.890
She needs some rest.

00:20:19.200 --> 00:20:19.960
What if

00:20:20.720 --> 00:20:23.000
she finds out we deceived her?

00:20:23.680 --> 00:20:24.960
She'll kill us.

00:20:27.440 --> 00:20:27.880
Erha,

00:20:28.280 --> 00:20:29.880
go check on Hua Xiaofei's room immediately.

00:20:29.880 --> 00:20:30.600
Yes, sir.

00:20:58.960 --> 00:20:59.600
Sir,

00:21:00.200 --> 00:21:02.400
Hua Xiaofei is sound asleep in her room.

00:21:03.440 --> 00:21:04.160
Go and take out

00:21:04.160 --> 00:21:05.440
all sharp objects from her room.

00:21:05.440 --> 00:21:07.720
And bowls too. Broken bowls can be used to cut wrists.

00:21:07.720 --> 00:21:08.520
Yes, sir.

00:22:06.240 --> 00:22:06.840
Sir.

00:22:10.720 --> 00:22:11.120
Well,

00:22:11.200 --> 00:22:11.640
Look,

00:22:12.760 --> 00:22:14.880
we must properly compensate her.

00:22:18.640 --> 00:22:19.500
Give her money.

00:22:20.000 --> 00:22:22.280
But how much money should we give

00:22:22.440 --> 00:22:23.440
to make her happy?

00:22:24.240 --> 00:22:25.970
According to Tang Dynasty law,

00:22:26.680 --> 00:22:29.480
the more severe the injury, the higher the compensation.

00:22:29.480 --> 00:22:31.000
Does Tang Dynasty law say anything

00:22:31.000 --> 00:22:34.460
about compensation for getting someone struck by lightning?

00:22:34.960 --> 00:22:36.480
Tang Dynasty law

00:22:37.160 --> 00:22:40.160
only covers man-made disasters, not natural calamities.

00:22:40.160 --> 00:22:41.560
So there's no precedent.

00:22:41.880 --> 00:22:43.480
Let's try another approach.

00:22:44.200 --> 00:22:46.680
What else does she like besides money?

00:22:52.280 --> 00:22:53.120
Otherwise...

00:22:53.360 --> 00:22:54.640
Let's make her think

00:22:54.760 --> 00:22:56.960
this was all just a dream.

00:23:18.680 --> 00:23:19.280
Oh my!

00:23:41.440 --> 00:23:43.880
Was I struck dead by lightning?

00:24:03.440 --> 00:24:04.300
Could it be that

00:24:05.840 --> 00:24:10.200
they're all candidates to be my future husband?

00:24:12.440 --> 00:24:15.040
Am I dreaming?

00:24:16.840 --> 00:24:17.440
No, wait.

00:24:18.680 --> 00:24:20.810
Aren't there enough options already?

00:24:22.720 --> 00:24:25.960
Heaven, can't you show me some mercy?

00:24:27.280 --> 00:24:29.960
I made one choice and got struck like this.

00:24:30.960 --> 00:24:32.890
And now there are even more of them.

00:24:33.600 --> 00:24:36.440
It doesn't matter how handsome they are.

00:24:55.680 --> 00:24:58.520
You may have high status,

00:25:05.200 --> 00:25:06.440
great wealth,

00:25:12.240 --> 00:25:13.640
and moral integrity.

00:25:17.960 --> 00:25:19.620
Handsome and extraordinary.

00:25:22.440 --> 00:25:23.900
I'm asking you a question.

00:25:29.240 --> 00:25:30.600
I can feel it.

00:25:31.240 --> 00:25:33.440
This feels too real.

00:25:35.440 --> 00:25:37.840
But I was clearly struck by lightning.

00:25:40.920 --> 00:25:43.760
Could it be that I was so obsessed with marriage

00:25:45.480 --> 00:25:48.440
that I kidnapped you all while sleepwalking?

00:26:09.520 --> 00:26:11.920
Where exactly did you come from?

00:26:14.880 --> 00:26:15.680
Where from?

00:26:16.720 --> 00:26:17.440
You.

00:26:21.920 --> 00:26:24.040
You two are behind this.

00:26:26.520 --> 00:26:27.720
Don't hit me. Stop it.

00:26:28.640 --> 00:26:30.680
I won't hit you. Don't run away.

00:26:32.440 --> 00:26:32.680
Stop hitting!

00:26:32.680 --> 00:26:33.280
Don't run!

00:26:35.480 --> 00:26:36.280
Stop running!

00:26:36.280 --> 00:26:38.080
If you don't hit us, we won't run.

00:26:38.400 --> 00:26:39.120
You

00:26:39.520 --> 00:26:40.180
Stop. Stop.

00:26:40.360 --> 00:26:41.090
Stand still.

00:26:41.880 --> 00:26:42.880
Stay right there.

00:26:44.400 --> 00:26:46.000
You actually tricked me.

00:26:46.360 --> 00:26:47.490
We just wanted to say

00:26:47.680 --> 00:26:50.360
you're always so fickle with romantic relationships,

00:26:50.360 --> 00:26:52.160
and wanted to teach you a lesson.

00:26:52.400 --> 00:26:53.960
But unexpectedly there was a strange phenomenon,

00:26:53.960 --> 00:26:55.160
and you got struck by lightning.

00:26:55.160 --> 00:26:55.960
That's right.

00:26:56.040 --> 00:26:58.640
So then we thought about how to make it up to you.

00:26:59.160 --> 00:27:02.200
So you two tricked me yesterday,

00:27:02.280 --> 00:27:04.000
and I got struck by lightning as a result,

00:27:04.000 --> 00:27:07.060
and now you're finding new ways to call me promiscuous,

00:27:07.400 --> 00:27:09.530
even sending four men to humiliate me?

00:27:11.200 --> 00:27:12.400
Not to humiliate you.

00:27:13.360 --> 00:27:14.490
It's compensation.

00:27:15.000 --> 00:27:16.160
In your eyes,

00:27:16.200 --> 00:27:18.530
am I just someone with no moral standards?

00:27:23.200 --> 00:27:24.860
I'm not staying here anymore.

00:27:25.000 --> 00:27:26.840
You really think that in all of Chang'an,

00:27:26.840 --> 00:27:28.500
I have to help you two cowards?

00:27:29.040 --> 00:27:30.760
Those two bastards.

00:27:40.480 --> 00:27:41.680
They're really gone.

00:27:42.440 --> 00:27:43.440
They really left.

00:27:46.160 --> 00:27:46.920
Are you okay?

00:27:47.680 --> 00:27:48.440
I'm fine.

00:27:49.400 --> 00:27:50.260
Please come in.

00:27:50.880 --> 00:27:52.040
How do you like it?

00:27:54.720 --> 00:27:56.120
This is our Yingchun Inn.

00:27:56.200 --> 00:27:58.000
The most luxurious room we have.

00:28:00.280 --> 00:28:01.280
It's acceptable.

00:28:01.600 --> 00:28:02.680
If you need anything, just let me know.

00:28:02.680 --> 00:28:04.340
If not, I'll head downstairs.

00:28:04.720 --> 00:28:05.160
You may go.

00:28:05.160 --> 00:28:05.690
Alright.

00:28:22.680 --> 00:28:26.480
Those two scoundrels may have deceived me,

00:28:27.880 --> 00:28:30.960
but some of what they said wasn't completely false.

00:28:35.840 --> 00:28:38.440
Finding a husband is such an important matter,

00:28:38.520 --> 00:28:39.840
yet those ancestors

00:28:40.200 --> 00:28:42.400
couldn't give me more clues?

00:29:00.000 --> 00:29:02.000
In this vast city of Chang'an,

00:29:03.480 --> 00:29:07.240
is there truly no place for me, Hua Xiaofei?

00:29:30.480 --> 00:29:31.880
In this city of Chang'an,

00:29:33.200 --> 00:29:35.660
is there really no woman willing to marry me?

00:29:37.360 --> 00:29:38.600
Have you seen Hua Xiaofei?

00:29:38.600 --> 00:29:39.440
No, I haven't.

00:29:39.440 --> 00:29:40.040
Excuse me,

00:29:40.040 --> 00:29:41.500
have you seen Hua Xiaofei?

00:29:41.680 --> 00:29:42.540
Never seen her.

00:29:43.240 --> 00:29:44.700
Have you seen Hua Xiaofei?

00:29:48.360 --> 00:29:49.160
Mr. Xu.

00:29:49.600 --> 00:29:50.440
Why are you stopping me?

00:29:50.440 --> 00:29:51.900
Have you seen Hua Xiaofei?

00:29:54.680 --> 00:29:57.440
Mr. Xu, let me ask you something.

00:29:57.440 --> 00:29:59.840
Who is this Hua Xiaofei to you?

00:29:59.840 --> 00:30:02.480
You've been running around for her time and again.

00:30:02.480 --> 00:30:05.140
Whenever there's the slightest issue with her,

00:30:05.200 --> 00:30:07.200
you become completely distraught.

00:30:08.360 --> 00:30:09.290
Get to the point.

00:30:09.640 --> 00:30:12.160
There are countless women in Chang'an,

00:30:12.520 --> 00:30:14.080
but in my opinion,

00:30:14.240 --> 00:30:15.640
in your eyes,

00:30:15.680 --> 00:30:18.440
there is only Hua Xiaofei.

00:30:37.920 --> 00:30:41.440
These ancestors didn't leave any clues.

00:30:41.760 --> 00:30:44.360
Which temple to pray at? Which incense to burn?

00:30:44.760 --> 00:30:47.040
They couldn't even leave me a sign.

00:30:50.640 --> 00:30:51.760
What is this?

00:30:55.280 --> 00:30:55.680
Charges.

00:30:55.680 --> 00:30:56.440
What does it say?

00:30:56.440 --> 00:30:56.970
Charges.

00:30:58.720 --> 00:31:01.000
Hua Xiaofei. She is Hua Xiaofei.

00:31:01.160 --> 00:31:02.440
Come look! It's her!

00:31:02.840 --> 00:31:04.480
Extorting money from innocent young women.

00:31:04.480 --> 00:31:06.440
Plotting against loyal court officials.

00:31:06.440 --> 00:31:07.600
Defaming the reputation of the Chamber of Commerce president.

00:31:07.600 --> 00:31:10.120
Spreading obscene and immoral influences. It's her!

00:31:10.120 --> 00:31:14.520
Beat her!

00:31:15.000 --> 00:31:15.480
Hit her!

00:31:18.440 --> 00:31:19.160
I'll kill you!

00:31:19.160 --> 00:31:19.760
Beat her!

00:31:20.480 --> 00:31:22.200
The heart is like the face.

00:31:22.760 --> 00:31:24.720
That's why we take great care of it.

00:31:24.920 --> 00:31:26.960
Once the face is not properly cleaned,

00:31:26.960 --> 00:31:28.920
it becomes dirty and stained.

00:31:29.240 --> 00:31:31.100
Once the heart is not cultivated,

00:31:31.480 --> 00:31:33.640
evil will enter it.

00:31:35.000 --> 00:31:35.920
Yang Debiao.

00:31:36.640 --> 00:31:37.200
Sir.

00:31:39.000 --> 00:31:40.960
May I ask why you've come to the Imperial Academy today,

00:31:40.960 --> 00:31:41.680
sir?

00:31:41.880 --> 00:31:43.760
I am the top investigator in Chang'an.

00:31:43.760 --> 00:31:45.820
I've solved nearly a thousand cases.

00:31:46.160 --> 00:31:47.560
I've already determined

00:31:47.680 --> 00:31:50.040
that this manifesto came from here.

00:31:55.520 --> 00:31:56.920
How did you determine

00:31:56.920 --> 00:31:59.040
that this manifesto came from our academy?

00:31:59.040 --> 00:32:00.300
I wrote the manifesto.

00:32:00.440 --> 00:32:02.440
I'll take responsibility for my own actions.

00:32:02.440 --> 00:32:03.960
Don't trouble the teacher.

00:32:03.960 --> 00:32:04.520
Good.

00:32:05.000 --> 00:32:06.200
I knew it was you.

00:32:07.040 --> 00:32:09.680
I order you to withdraw all the manifestos immediately.

00:32:09.680 --> 00:32:11.040
The manifestos can be withdrawn,

00:32:11.040 --> 00:32:13.760
but everyone in Chang'an already knows about it.

00:32:13.760 --> 00:32:16.160
How will you withdraw it from their hearts?

00:32:16.200 --> 00:32:18.060
Why did you write this manifesto?

00:32:18.200 --> 00:32:19.920
Teacher, Hua Xiaofei

00:32:20.400 --> 00:32:23.040
has turned Chang'an city upside down.

00:32:23.240 --> 00:32:24.640
As a scholar,

00:32:24.640 --> 00:32:26.440
shouldn't I alert the public?

00:32:26.520 --> 00:32:27.640
Alert the public?

00:32:28.040 --> 00:32:30.200
What you've written is complete nonsense.

00:32:30.200 --> 00:32:30.920
Is that so?

00:32:31.360 --> 00:32:33.490
Then which part of what I said is wrong?

00:32:33.880 --> 00:32:35.480
If what I said is truly wrong,

00:32:35.480 --> 00:32:37.540
are all the people in Chang'an fools?

00:32:37.680 --> 00:32:40.140
How could they respond so readily to my call?

00:32:41.680 --> 00:32:43.160
Sir, Officer Xu.

00:32:45.000 --> 00:32:47.600
How could you commit such a disrespectful act?

00:32:52.760 --> 00:32:53.290
Yang Lin.

00:32:54.000 --> 00:32:55.880
Tell everyone not to stay in the mansion.

00:32:55.880 --> 00:32:56.840
Go out and search.

00:32:56.840 --> 00:32:57.840
You must find her.

00:32:58.400 --> 00:32:59.400
But sir,

00:32:59.840 --> 00:33:01.770
the four elders are waiting for you

00:33:01.840 --> 00:33:03.840
to discuss the Flower Queen selection.

00:33:03.840 --> 00:33:05.280
If you don't go now, you'll be late.

00:33:05.280 --> 00:33:05.960
I know.

00:33:06.520 --> 00:33:07.680
I'll go by myself.

00:33:08.520 --> 00:33:10.050
You go find Hua Xiaofei too.

00:33:10.120 --> 00:33:10.600
Sir,

00:33:11.000 --> 00:33:12.160
you're going to the guild?

00:33:12.160 --> 00:33:13.840
I must follow along.

00:33:14.120 --> 00:33:15.880
One more person is always better than one less.

00:33:15.880 --> 00:33:17.200
Stop talking. Go now.

00:33:17.960 --> 00:33:18.480
Yes.

00:33:26.280 --> 00:33:27.480
Lift the sedan chair.

00:33:27.960 --> 00:33:29.040
Go find them quickly.

00:33:29.040 --> 00:33:29.640
Yes.

00:33:45.360 --> 00:33:47.200
Fang Lihen.

00:33:48.280 --> 00:33:49.200
Sir Fang.

00:33:49.880 --> 00:33:51.920
Sir, Mr. Fang.

00:33:52.680 --> 00:33:53.880
Take care on your way.

00:33:57.600 --> 00:33:59.400
How's it going? Did you find her?

00:34:02.880 --> 00:34:04.240
I know I was wrong.

00:34:04.640 --> 00:34:06.240
I will leave this place forever.

00:34:06.240 --> 00:34:07.680
Leave all of you forever.

00:34:08.000 --> 00:34:08.760
Xiaofei

00:34:09.679 --> 00:34:11.040
What does she mean by that?

00:34:11.040 --> 00:34:12.600
She's not thinking of hurting herself, is she?

00:34:12.600 --> 00:34:13.120
I...

00:34:13.520 --> 00:34:15.850
I thought she just didn't want us anymore.

00:34:17.560 --> 00:34:19.159
Then hurry up and go find her!

00:34:21.040 --> 00:34:23.159
By the way, if you find her,

00:34:23.440 --> 00:34:25.639
make sure she can stay in Chang'an City.

00:34:28.639 --> 00:34:30.170
Yang Lin, you go search too.

00:34:30.440 --> 00:34:30.920
Yes.

00:34:46.600 --> 00:34:47.600
Where's the gong?

00:35:00.360 --> 00:35:01.820
What's all this money for?

00:35:02.880 --> 00:35:03.810
What's going on?

00:35:06.360 --> 00:35:09.520
I am Xu Ziqi, the top bounty hunter in Chang'an.

00:35:09.800 --> 00:35:10.600
A few days ago,

00:35:10.760 --> 00:35:13.760
you ladies arranged a blind date between Hua Xiaofei and me.

00:35:13.760 --> 00:35:15.040
I was the one who broke our appointment first.

00:35:15.040 --> 00:35:16.040
Please everyone,

00:35:16.600 --> 00:35:18.530
don't give Hua Xiaofei a hard time.

00:35:19.360 --> 00:35:22.920
So I apologize to all you ladies here.

00:35:23.360 --> 00:35:24.720
All the silver paid for matchmaking

00:35:24.720 --> 00:35:26.360
will be returned to everyone.

00:35:26.360 --> 00:35:28.020
Please take your silver back.

00:35:30.000 --> 00:35:32.360
Sir, do you think we want money?

00:35:32.480 --> 00:35:34.280
What we want is you, sir!

00:35:35.000 --> 00:35:35.840
That's right!

00:35:36.440 --> 00:35:38.440
Sir, I want to date you.

00:35:38.600 --> 00:35:39.960
I want to meet you for matchmaking.

00:35:39.960 --> 00:35:42.160
I want to find love with you.

00:35:42.400 --> 00:35:42.880
Yes!

00:35:43.240 --> 00:35:45.000
We want to pursue love with you.

00:35:45.720 --> 00:35:47.480
Sir, please meet with us for matchmaking.

00:35:47.480 --> 00:35:48.080
Sir!

00:35:48.160 --> 00:35:50.120
If I agree to meet with all of you,

00:35:50.480 --> 00:35:52.400
will you stop bothering Hua Xiaofei?

00:35:52.400 --> 00:35:52.920
Yes.

00:35:53.040 --> 00:35:55.000
We definitely won't trouble her anymore.

00:35:55.000 --> 00:35:55.530
Alright.

00:35:55.920 --> 00:35:57.440
Great!

00:35:57.480 --> 00:36:01.720
Blind date.

00:36:11.280 --> 00:36:13.040
I'm sorry. I'm a bit excited.

00:36:13.080 --> 00:36:13.720
Master Xu.

00:36:13.880 --> 00:36:14.320
Miss,

00:36:15.040 --> 00:36:16.040
please calm down.

00:36:16.320 --> 00:36:17.320
I can't calm down.

00:36:17.440 --> 00:36:19.240
You know, I really admire you.

00:36:19.400 --> 00:36:20.240
So many girls

00:36:20.240 --> 00:36:21.560
like you.

00:36:21.640 --> 00:36:23.480
I truly admire your talent.

00:36:23.480 --> 00:36:24.000
Really?

00:36:26.920 --> 00:36:28.600
Is this your father?

00:36:29.440 --> 00:36:29.800
No.

00:36:30.120 --> 00:36:32.780
This is the famous painter Mr. Wu from Chang'an.

00:36:32.800 --> 00:36:35.600
I specially invited Mr. Wu to paint for me and you.

00:36:35.800 --> 00:36:38.260
Let's paint a portrait of us two as a memento.

00:36:44.360 --> 00:36:45.640
I'm so sorry, Mr. Xu.

00:36:45.640 --> 00:36:47.040
I don't know what's wrong with my hand.

00:36:47.040 --> 00:36:48.960
It's just not cooperating today.

00:36:49.120 --> 00:36:50.720
I apologize for my rudeness.

00:36:50.960 --> 00:36:54.320
I just wanted you to use your beautiful hand

00:36:54.480 --> 00:36:56.540
to give me your autograph, would you?

00:36:56.600 --> 00:36:57.480
Please.

00:36:57.640 --> 00:36:58.880
I really like you.

00:36:59.000 --> 00:37:00.080
Please sign for me.

00:37:00.240 --> 00:37:02.640
Mr. Xu, I'm begging you for your signature.

00:37:34.720 --> 00:37:36.120
I'm so hungry.

00:37:38.040 --> 00:37:40.080
I really want to eat something.

00:37:46.480 --> 00:37:47.640
Pretty lady,

00:37:48.320 --> 00:37:49.120
why don't

00:37:49.320 --> 00:37:51.720
we brothers have some fun with her tonight?

00:37:55.360 --> 00:37:56.440
Not bad at all.

00:38:07.440 --> 00:38:08.080
You...

00:38:08.080 --> 00:38:09.720
You... don't come

00:38:11.640 --> 00:38:12.300
any closer!

00:38:12.400 --> 00:38:13.440
Come on.

00:38:22.040 --> 00:38:23.400
It's okay, it's me.

00:38:26.400 --> 00:38:28.460
Don't be afraid, everything's fine.

00:38:38.760 --> 00:38:40.020
You scared me to death.

00:38:44.000 --> 00:38:45.360
Chang'an is too big.

00:38:45.800 --> 00:38:47.260
Hard to find my way around.

00:38:47.480 --> 00:38:48.440
I'm late.

00:38:49.560 --> 00:38:50.320
I'm sorry.

00:38:58.800 --> 00:38:59.440
Well...

00:39:02.320 --> 00:39:04.720
What are you laughing at? Stop laughing.

00:39:07.440 --> 00:39:08.120
Um...

00:39:12.240 --> 00:39:13.400
I'm hungry.

00:39:14.480 --> 00:39:15.160
Well then,

00:39:16.080 --> 00:39:18.210
let me take you somewhere to eat, okay?

00:39:21.040 --> 00:39:21.570
Let's go.

00:39:23.400 --> 00:39:24.040
I...

00:39:25.240 --> 00:39:27.120
I'm too hungry to walk.

00:39:33.280 --> 00:39:33.920
Fine.

00:39:38.080 --> 00:39:38.880
Get on.

00:40:03.760 --> 00:40:05.560
Isn't this Mr. Xu?

00:40:07.080 --> 00:40:07.800
Please, come in.

00:40:07.800 --> 00:40:09.000
Got your energy back?

00:40:10.560 --> 00:40:11.090
Let's go.

00:40:11.360 --> 00:40:12.090
Please, sir.

00:40:22.120 --> 00:40:22.800
All of these

00:40:22.960 --> 00:40:25.280
are your favorite dishes, sir.

00:40:27.440 --> 00:40:28.920
Here, please enjoy.

00:40:31.520 --> 00:40:31.920
Delicious.

00:40:31.920 --> 00:40:32.400
Here.

00:40:33.360 --> 00:40:33.960
Thank you.

00:40:35.040 --> 00:40:35.720
Try this.

00:40:42.800 --> 00:40:44.400
You've come at the perfect time.

00:40:44.400 --> 00:40:46.560
These clothes have just been washed.

00:40:46.840 --> 00:40:48.600
They'll be useful at Anpingle.

00:40:49.800 --> 00:40:50.560
Thank you for your kindness.

00:40:50.560 --> 00:40:51.690
I'm truly grateful.

00:40:51.880 --> 00:40:52.480
However...

00:40:52.480 --> 00:40:54.520
Mr. Xu, there's no need for formality.

00:40:54.520 --> 00:40:56.840
You've taken on Anpingle by yourself,

00:40:56.840 --> 00:40:58.360
sheltering the poor and needy.

00:40:58.360 --> 00:41:00.800
It's truly admirable.

00:41:03.800 --> 00:41:05.640
With prices soaring these days,

00:41:06.120 --> 00:41:08.120
expenses are three times what they used to be.

00:41:08.120 --> 00:41:09.800
Your shop isn't wealthy to begin with.

00:41:09.800 --> 00:41:12.040
Please don't subsidize Anpingle anymore.

00:41:12.040 --> 00:41:13.520
Sir, please don't say that.

00:41:13.520 --> 00:41:15.920
I just want to do what little I can.

00:41:16.600 --> 00:41:17.560
Please enjoy your meal.

00:41:17.560 --> 00:41:19.000
I'll take my leave now.

00:41:27.920 --> 00:41:29.040
Anpingle?

00:41:29.400 --> 00:41:31.000
Xu Ziqi, what's going on?

00:41:32.120 --> 00:41:32.920
Well, it's

00:41:33.440 --> 00:41:34.840
a house outside the city.

00:41:36.600 --> 00:41:37.520
A house?

00:41:37.840 --> 00:41:38.900
During my patrols,

00:41:39.000 --> 00:41:40.720
I often see homeless people.

00:41:41.400 --> 00:41:43.560
So I thought they could stay there,

00:41:44.160 --> 00:41:46.360
at least to have shelter from the elements.

00:41:46.360 --> 00:41:48.360
So you're doing charity work.

00:41:48.880 --> 00:41:50.320
From what the boss said,

00:41:51.000 --> 00:41:52.600
you've taken in many people.

00:41:53.480 --> 00:41:55.400
So you must have a

00:41:55.880 --> 00:41:57.240
very large house?

00:41:58.240 --> 00:42:00.240
It's my family's ancestral home.

00:42:00.520 --> 00:42:03.080
After my great-grandfather acquired this house,

00:42:03.080 --> 00:42:05.120
he sacrificed his life for the country.

00:42:05.120 --> 00:42:07.920
For three generations, my family has had only one heir.

00:42:07.920 --> 00:42:09.520
Now we have this empty house

00:42:10.400 --> 00:42:11.800
with no one living there.

00:42:12.840 --> 00:42:16.000
My ancestors were always concerned about the common people.

00:42:16.000 --> 00:42:16.880
So I thought,

00:42:17.440 --> 00:42:19.640
if I could use this house to do some good,

00:42:20.240 --> 00:42:22.300
it would honor my ancestors' memory.

00:42:22.600 --> 00:42:24.480
So in other words,

00:42:25.080 --> 00:42:27.610
you're actually a rich person with a mansion.

00:42:28.240 --> 00:42:30.240
Hua Xiaofei,

00:42:30.960 --> 00:42:33.020
why do you only focus on these things?

00:42:33.800 --> 00:42:35.520
No, I'm sorry.

00:42:36.720 --> 00:42:37.480
You

00:42:38.960 --> 00:42:40.000
know what I mean.

00:42:40.760 --> 00:42:41.890
You're poor, right?

00:42:42.520 --> 00:42:43.160
Yes.

00:42:44.240 --> 00:42:46.160
No, what I meant was

00:42:46.560 --> 00:42:49.360
so that's where all your money goes.

00:42:49.760 --> 00:42:51.880
Yes, and I'm up to my neck in debt.

00:42:53.000 --> 00:42:53.800
That's true.

00:42:54.640 --> 00:42:58.440
Taking care of so many elderly and orphaned children

00:42:58.440 --> 00:43:00.040
must cost a fortune.

00:43:00.800 --> 00:43:03.240
Why don't you keep some for yourself?

00:43:03.320 --> 00:43:05.920
Three generations of my family have sacrificed for our country.

00:43:05.920 --> 00:43:07.780
All for the people's well-being.

00:43:07.840 --> 00:43:09.560
How could I be stingy?

00:43:12.880 --> 00:43:13.940
You're such a fool.

00:43:25.760 --> 00:43:26.360
Master Xu.

00:43:26.920 --> 00:43:28.850
Thank you for protecting all of us.

00:43:29.240 --> 00:43:31.040
Let me handle this small matter.

00:43:45.040 --> 00:43:46.360
Do you have a fever?

00:43:46.480 --> 00:43:47.540
Your face is so red.

00:43:49.280 --> 00:43:50.040
No.

00:43:52.440 --> 00:43:55.120
I've been practicing a type of internal martial arts lately.

00:43:55.120 --> 00:43:56.520
Whenever I use this skill,

00:43:56.520 --> 00:43:57.360
this happens.

00:44:03.440 --> 00:44:05.960
Where do you plan to go after this?

00:44:06.520 --> 00:44:07.440
I don't know.

00:44:09.000 --> 00:44:09.880
Why don't you

00:44:11.320 --> 00:44:12.850
just find someone to marry?

00:44:13.800 --> 00:44:14.320
Me?

00:44:16.080 --> 00:44:17.080
Who would want me?

00:44:18.520 --> 00:44:19.080
True.

00:44:19.440 --> 00:44:20.900
Who would want you anyway?

00:44:21.440 --> 00:44:24.500
You're the last person who should talk, you lonely dog.

00:44:26.240 --> 00:44:26.800
Who?

00:44:30.840 --> 00:44:31.480
Xu Ziqi!

00:44:33.040 --> 00:44:34.700
Where did that dart come from?

00:44:37.440 --> 00:44:39.080
What's going on?

00:44:40.040 --> 00:44:40.800
You...

00:44:42.480 --> 00:44:42.880
Stay

00:44:42.880 --> 00:44:43.480
still!